name: 3 X Small dog identity tags
description:
Set of 3 unique pet ID tags to help prevent your dog getting lost or stolen

Ideal for small dogs eg: cavalier king charles spaniels, jack russells, bichon frise, border terrier, lakeland terrier, maltese, poodle, miniture pincher, pekinese, pomeranian, pug, schnauzer, shih tzu, skye terrier, welsh corgi, west highland white terrier, yorkshire terrier cavajacks, cavapoos, etc 

Suitable for occasional use such as going on holiday or walkies in an unfamiliar place

Wipe clean - waterproof, rain proof, mud proof and rollin in something nasty proof!

Tells other people who to call if the dog gets lost (recommend a mobile number). 

Tells people your dog is microchipped making it less desirable to thieves and puppy farmers

When you order I will send you an email and ask you to provide contact details and a picture of your dog

Postage is FREE in mainland UK
